<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Selamat Datang di AlphaMart</title>
    <!-- Font dari Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* 
          COLOR PALETTE DARI LOGO INDOMARET
          Merah: #D8251E
          Biru: #0053A0
          Kuning: #FDCB00
        */

        :root {
            --color-red: #D8251E;
            --color-blue: #0053A0;
            --color-yellow: #FDCB00;
            --text-dark: #333;
            --text-light: #fff;
            --bg-light: #f8f9fa;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .hero {
            background-color: var(--color-blue);
            color: var(--text-light);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--color-red);
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #b01e18;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .features {
            padding: 60px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .features h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: var(--color-blue);
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .feature-item {
            flex-basis: 30%;
        }

        .feature-item .icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            stroke: var(--color-red);
        }

        .feature-item h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .promo {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .promo h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: var(--color-blue);
        }

        .promo-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .product-card {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 250px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .product-card img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .product-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .product-card .price {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--color-red);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: var(--color-blue);
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #00417e;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: var(--color-blue);
            color: var(--text-light);
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include("./partials/navbar") %>

        <main>
            <section class="hero">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Selamat Datang di AlphaMart</h1>
                    <p>Solusi belanja hemat dan lengkap untuk kebutuhan harian Anda.</p>
                    <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">Belanja Sekarang</a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="features">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Kenapa Belanja di AlphaMart?</h2>
                    <div class="features-grid">
                        <div class="feature-item">
